<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>refhub verificationCode email</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard/dist/web/static/pretendard.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Pretendard', sans-serif;
      height: 100vh;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      background-color: #FFFFFF;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 40px;
      background: #FFFFFF;
      border: 1px solid #F9FAF9;
      text-align: left;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
    }
    .logo {
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .logo img {
      height: 20px;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      color: #282828;
      margin: 0;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
    }
    hr {
      width: 100px;
      border: none;
      border-top: 1.6px solid #FBBC05;
      margin: 10px 0 20px 0;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .content {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #282828;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
    }
    .verification-code {
      display: block;
      background-color: #1ABC9C;
      color: white;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      width: 200px;
      height: 60px;
      line-height: 60px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 10px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .note {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #8A8D8A;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo">
      <img src="cid:logo" alt="RefHub 로고">
    </div>
    <h1>레퍼브 비밀번호 재설정 인증 번호</h1>
    <hr>
    <div class="content">
      <p><strong><%= name %></strong> 님,<br>
        레퍼브 비밀번호 재설정을 위한 인증 번호를 보내드립니다.<br>
        레퍼브에서 아래의 인증 번호를 입력해주세요.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="verification-code"><%= authCode %></div>
    <p class="note">*인증 번호는 10분 동안 유효합니다.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
